{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Dungeons & Dragons'' 3rd edition monsters}} {{see also|List of Dungeons & Dragons monsters}}
''[[Dungeons & Dragons]]'' 3rd Edition (see [[editions of Dungeons & Dragons|editions of ''Dungeons & Dragons'']]) was released in 2000. The first book containing monsters to be published was the ''[[Monster Manual]]'', released along with the other two "core" rulebooks. [[Wizards of the Coast]] officially discontinued the 3rd Edition line upon the release of a revision, known as version 3.5, in 2003, with the ''[[List of Dungeons & Dragons 3.5 edition monsters#WTC 17755 – Monster Manual (2003)|Monster Manual]]'' reprinted for the revised edition.
