==Most prominent summits==
{{GeoGroup|section=Most prominent summits}}
Of the most prominent summits of Wyoming, [[Cloud Peak]] and [[Gannett Peak]] both exceed {{convert|2000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence.  Those two peaks and [[Grand Teton]] are ultra-prominent summits with more than {{convert|1500|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence.  Nine peaks exceed {{convert|1000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence.
{{clear}}
